comments: The best instructor I\'ve ever had!

She is by far one of the most dedicated teachers I have ever seen. Extremely knowledgeable, though she teaches tough, she makes it easy to listen and learn. She brings real world projects to her classroom and is willing to go the extra mile for her students to succeed. I am going to take every class she offers, no other teacher can compare.

She\'s one of the best teachers I have ever had. There\'s no way to express her dedication to teaching and her willingness to help. Take her, don\'t think about taking anyone else because you will regret it.
Grat instructor. Very humorous, uses multiple teaching techniques, goes the extra mile to help students achieve their educational goals.
She\'s an expert in the art and will happily assist you in any techniques or other instruction. I highly recommend taking a welding class with her instead of Figg since she seems much more committed.
